Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:02.60,0:00:05.33,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,GA緊張刺激 老太婆Bang!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:08.22,0:00:11.43,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,GA慌慌張張 山姥Gun!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:14.34,0:00:16.61,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,銀河天使A
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:17.08,0:00:21.64,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,快點來啊 賓果! 中大獎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:22.88,0:00:28.19,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,滿面笑容 PicoPico 一口氣飛到月亮
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:28.19,0:00:28.81,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,呀呵
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:28.89,0:00:34.12,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,一天一餐 活力充沛 喝牛奶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:34.90,0:00:40.27,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就算是外星人也能輕鬆發出電波交朋友
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:40.32,0:00:41.68,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,古今東西！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:42.98,0:00:46.57,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,回憶是熱帶地區
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:46.87,0:00:49.44,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,夏威夷衫好漂亮
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:49.71,0:00:51.84,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,啊 被看穿了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:51.95,0:00:56.28,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,趕緊破涕為笑
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:56.35,0:00:59.68,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,從石頭開始猜拳
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:59.75,0:01:02.39,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,緊張刺激的雲霄飛車
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:02.46,0:01:05.34,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,愛和勇氣和夢想紙摺扇
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:05.39,0:01:10.72,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,心的渦輪加速前進
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:10.74,0:01:11.65,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Bang！Bang！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:11.67,0:01:13.13,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,吃吧 瘋吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:13.20,0:01:14.52,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,哇喔！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:14.54,0:01:17.05,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,暢行無阻的護照
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:17.07,0:01:22.20,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,充滿戲劇性又浪漫的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:22.23,0:01:26.04,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,大冒險
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:00.60,0:00:00.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,By VOYOOFPDK
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:30.75,0:01:35.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,再見了我們的陶製茶壺蒸湯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:36.22,0:01:38.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,媽媽 唸這本故事書給我聽
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:39.36,0:01:40.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,又是這本嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:40.83,0:01:42.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,人家喜歡這個故事嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:42.96,0:01:44.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那媽媽開始唸囉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:45.27,0:01:46.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,很久很久以前
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:46.93,0:01:49.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在某個國家個很大的城堡裡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:49.34,0:01:51.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,住著一個國王
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:53.31,0:01:56.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這個城鎮好熱鬧 看起來好好玩喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:56.31,0:01:59.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,香草 我們去玩一下吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:59.98,0:02:01.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,梅爾優
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:01.22,0:02:05.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,都因為你讓我們大幅延誤了歸隊的時間
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:05.62,0:02:09.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,定期連絡也沒有做 我們應該立刻回去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:10.16,0:02:11.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那裡有好玩的東西
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:11.59,0:02:12.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,梅爾優
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:31.58,0:02:32.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好奇怪的臉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:40.75,0:02:43.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,請問 我做了什麼嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:44.39,0:02:47.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在這個國家侮辱身為國王的我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:47.90,0:02:50.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是最重的罪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:50.13,0:02:51.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,國王？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:51.20,0:02:52.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你是國王？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:54.50,0:02:56.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那張臉果然很爆笑
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:57.24,0:02:58.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,沒有斟酌減刑的餘地
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:59.01,0:03:01.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我要將你處以極刑
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:02.04,0:03:04.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,看來梅爾優真的覺得他很好笑
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:04.78,0:03:06.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你們也要關起來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:07.01,0:03:08.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,請等一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:08.12,0:03:10.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,笑的人是那個少根筋沒大腦的女孩
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:10.95,0:03:12.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,跟我們無關
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:12.75,0:03:13.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,閉嘴
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:13.65,0:03:16.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你們在一旁沒有加以阻止一樣有罪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:16.49,0:03:17.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,怎麼這樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:18.16,0:03:22.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,如果沒有那個恐怖的詛咒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:22.33,0:03:23.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,詛咒？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:24.13,0:03:27.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,以前在森林裡的一座城堡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:27.17,0:03:31.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,有一位美女被關在那裡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:31.71,0:03:34.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,城主雖然長得很醜
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:34.51,0:03:39.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可是他溫柔的心感動了美女 兩人於是墜入情網
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:40.08,0:03:42.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,接著生下來的 就是我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:43.25,0:03:45.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這樣就結束了嗎？那麼詛咒呢？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:46.12,0:03:49.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我完全沒有繼承我母親的美貌
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:50.02,0:03:51.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這不是詛咒是什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:51.96,0:03:54.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這種想法不太好吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:55.73,0:03:57.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,明天行刑
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:59.17,0:04:03.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,香草 偶爾要來看我喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:03.64,0:04:07.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那個運氣超好的梅爾優居然會碰上厄運
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:07.24,0:04:10.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,目前還是跟她保持距離比較好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:10.95,0:04:12.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我得想想辦法
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:12.51,0:04:13.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,香草
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:14.28,0:04:15.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,快走
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:16.28,0:04:19.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就是這裡 不可以碰周圍的機械
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:21.06,0:04:26.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不用說 我也知道善良的香草要做什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:26.63,0:04:30.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不好了 得救出梅爾優才行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:30.10,0:04:33.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可是現在的我又能做什麼呢？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:33.13,0:04:36.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不過又不能袖手旁觀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:36.14,0:04:38.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,至少要幫忙想想辦法
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:42.48,0:04:45.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什麼？你能沉默地吃完一條大條的壽司捲？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:45.78,0:04:49.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不行 不行 我不能隨便給你食物
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:50.75,0:04:52.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,得想想辦法才行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:54.02,0:04:57.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,為什麼城裡的人不會覺得好笑呢？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:57.29,0:04:58.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,因為他們習慣了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:59.03,0:05:00.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,打擾了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:01.06,0:05:02.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,香草
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:02.30,0:05:04.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我們是來送梅爾優的伙食的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:05.00,0:05:06.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我要吃囉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:07.07,0:05:08.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,梅爾優
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:08.07,0:05:11.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,幸好通訊器沒有被他們發現
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:11.24,0:05:14.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我在你手上的麵包裡塞了一把銼刀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:14.68,0:05:16.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你應該知道是做什麼用的吧？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:17.81,0:05:21.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,知道 就是把鐵質磨出來吃 讓身體更健康對不對？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:21.95,0:05:24.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,從遙遠的山頂往下看
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:24.08,0:05:25.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你是白癡嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:25.35,0:05:29.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那是要讓你拿來鋸斷鐵窗逃獄用的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:29.86,0:05:32.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,請小心那個守衛喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:32.93,0:05:34.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,現在就要鋸嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:34.09,0:05:36.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,明天早上就要行刑了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:36.40,0:05:38.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,快點鋸
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:52.91,0:05:57.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,想趁城堡遭到不明破壞時逃獄 沒那麼簡單
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:59.15,0:06:02.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不 剛才我只是因為回想起一些很好笑的事而已
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:02.22,0:06:03.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:03.36,0:06:07.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你想起的那個人想必有一張很好笑的臉吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:07.73,0:06:09.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,因為損壞太嚴重了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:09.43,0:06:15.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,原因是香草精心研磨的銼刀和梅爾優白癡行為
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:15.10,0:06:16.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,才沒有被揭穿
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:16.70,0:06:19.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這下梅爾優要逃獄恐怕
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:20.81,0:06:22.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,香草
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:24.51,0:06:27.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,難道你打算挖逃獄用的地道？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:28.15,0:06:31.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,想不到越笑運氣越差
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:31.69,0:06:34.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,幸運女神到來了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:35.06,0:06:37.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,請感謝香草
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:37.39,0:06:41.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我親眼看著她挖了一條逃獄地道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:41.56,0:06:44.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,只用一根湯匙 簡直像魔法一樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:44.90,0:06:47.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,簡直像某部動畫裡演的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:47.40,0:06:50.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,現在剛好挖到梅爾優你的腳邊附近
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:50.67,0:06:52.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你就趁機
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:52.21,0:06:54.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,要我來幫忙挖通是吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:54.61,0:06:57.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不 你現在什麼都別做比較好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:58.01,0:07:00.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,對不起 請借我鏟子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:00.78,0:07:03.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你要鏟子幹什麼？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:03.25,0:07:04.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,馬上就會還你的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:05.09,0:07:06.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我要挖了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:06.52,0:07:08.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,聽得見嗎？梅爾優
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:12.19,0:07:14.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,連這裡都像某部動畫一樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:21.17,0:07:23.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,即使發生了將半個城市都毀了的大災難
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:23.60,0:07:25.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,明天還是要行刑
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:26.17,0:07:30.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,為了讓你知道我受的屈辱有多深
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:30.08,0:07:31.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,怎麼這樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:31.38,0:07:35.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,別看我這樣 我在故鄉可是得過「凝視賭笑」冠軍耶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:35.55,0:07:36.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那又怎樣？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:38.42,0:07:41.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,笑到這種地步 真想頒個勳章給你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:42.99,0:07:44.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,請等一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:47.76,0:07:48.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什麼？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:48.63,0:07:52.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,梅爾優現在出現在你面前的是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:52.57,0:07:59.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,香草和我用遺失文明的不完整資料製造的空間移轉裝置
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:59.34,0:08:01.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,請你通過那個走過來這邊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:01.91,0:08:04.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但是 移動的目的地目前還沒有固定
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:05.01,0:08:08.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,所以命名為「不知去哪裡的門」
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:08.08,0:08:09.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,請務必小心謹慎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:13.09,0:08:14.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,糟糕
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:14.15,0:08:17.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這個裝置果然還是不穩定
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:19.53,0:08:20.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不見了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:28.80,0:08:31.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,通過約定之門的人啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:31.97,0:08:34.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我們的名字叫「離譜道路」
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:35.18,0:08:40.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你是來詢問我們問題的吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:40.48,0:08:43.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我們會一五一十回答你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:43.62,0:08:47.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,意思是任何問題都會回答我嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:47.49,0:08:48.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,沒錯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:50.06,0:08:54.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那我就問囉 你們看起來都是男的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:54.66,0:08:56.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你們會不會覺得很苦悶？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:56.13,0:08:57.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,汗臭味很難聞？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:57.93,0:08:59.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,或是希望有女人緣？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:59.60,0:09:01.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,或是覺得很寂寞？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:06.11,0:09:10.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,總覺得梅爾優只要一做什麼事 監獄就會更加遭到破壞...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:10.88,0:09:14.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,恐怖的梅爾優櫻葉17歲
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:14.15,0:09:15.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,儀式結束
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:16.88,0:09:19.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,今天是破壞監獄的日子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:20.79,0:09:23.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,香草 難道剛才的都是你？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:23.36,0:09:24.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:25.83,0:09:28.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不論是監獄被燒還是城堡被半毀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:28.96,0:09:31.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我一定要行刑
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:31.53,0:09:34.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,國王 我已經洗心革面了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:34.60,0:09:37.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你看 我沒有笑吧 對不對？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:37.90,0:09:39.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是嗎 是嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:39.71,0:09:41.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,準備好了嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:43.34,0:09:47.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,看吧 這就是我國的生化科技所孕育出的生命體
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:47.88,0:09:49.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,野獸4號
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:49.72,0:09:54.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,而這就是嘲笑我的人必須接受的殘酷極刑
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:57.89,0:10:01.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你說的極刑不是死刑 而是變得像那隻貓一樣嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:02.83,0:10:07.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,大部分的觀眾都應該早就知道這裡說的不是死刑吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:08.00,0:10:12.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,怎麼樣？你也會變成連蒼蠅都不屑沾一下的腐臭臉龐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:12.67,0:10:16.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不論走到哪裡都會被小孩取笑
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:16.78,0:10:19.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你又何必這麼自虐呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:20.45,0:10:26.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,話說回來 既然有這種技術把自己的臉修整一下比較好吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:30.39,0:10:32.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,行刑 野獸4號
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:36.90,0:10:37.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,怎麼回事？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:38.67,0:10:40.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,所有人都不准動
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:40.13,0:10:43.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,否則國王的腦袋就會搬家喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:43.30,0:10:46.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可惡 每個人都看不起我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:46.41,0:10:47.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不要再耍脾氣了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:48.48,0:10:50.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你身為一國之君
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:51.04,0:10:53.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不能被外表所蒙蔽
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:53.81,0:10:56.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,重要的是要有一顆美麗的心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:56.68,0:10:59.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,沒錯 外表是不足為道的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:59.52,0:11:02.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,拘泥於外表的人是很沒水準的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:02.66,0:11:05.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不要捧著台詞照唸
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:07.33,0:11:10.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,對了 剛才你說這是野獸4號
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:10.53,0:11:14.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,當然還有1號2號3號囉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:17.24,0:11:20.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,媽媽 我明白了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:20.37,0:11:23.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,人果然得靠長相 對吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:23.08,0:11:24.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不對
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:25.01,0:11:27.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,外表的美總有一天會衰老
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:27.98,0:11:29.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,最後能夠左右一切的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:30.22,0:11:31.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是錢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:31.45,0:11:32.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,錢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:38.39,0:11:41.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,所謂能笑就能招來福氣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:41.26,0:11:43.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這次這樣算不錯了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:44.50,0:11:45.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,一點都不好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:46.20,0:11:47.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,今天的話題
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:48.00,0:11:48.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,(辛苦了)
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:48.54,0:11:50.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那些字看起來好沒精神喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:50.30,0:11:53.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,「辛苦了」我看你比較辛苦吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:53.77,0:11:55.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可能是太累了吧(「累」音同「辛苦了」)
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:56.08,0:11:56.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,辛苦了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:56.81,0:11:57.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,辛苦了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:57.61,0:11:58.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,辛苦了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:58.35,0:11:59.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,辛苦了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:59.58,0:12:00.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,辛苦了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:00.61,0:12:04.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,所以 寫那個看板的人一定是最沒精神的香草
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:04.28,0:12:06.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,現在是在決定這個的嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:06.29,0:12:08.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,總之 香草獲得一個坐墊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:08.69,0:12:10.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,其實已經是準班底了？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:19.90,0:12:21.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我想要知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:21.87,0:12:25.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在我忙著處理雜務時所發生的事情真相
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:26.34,0:12:27.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我也一樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:27.44,0:12:30.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,當我在別的行星執行任務的時候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:30.61,0:12:32.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,究竟出了什麼事？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:32.21,0:12:37.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那麼就用基地內監視攝影機拍攝到的影像來說明吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:43.76,0:12:46.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,事情是從這個箱子開始
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:49.66,0:12:51.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,請小心一點喔 佛特
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:51.93,0:12:55.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,別看它這樣 它也是個遺失文明
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:56.40,0:12:59.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我知道啦 我又不是新來的隊員
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:01.04,0:13:02.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,說的也是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:04.78,0:13:06.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,忍耐一下 中校
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:06.25,0:13:07.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,話雖然這麼說
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:12.69,0:13:14.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好痛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:14.32,0:13:15.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,喂 這下該怎麼辦？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:15.92,0:13:18.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,遺失文明的箱子被打開了啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:19.26,0:13:20.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我的腰
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:20.49,0:13:23.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,得快點去醫院
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:24.06,0:13:25.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,喂 你還好吧？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:26.27,0:13:28.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我要早退 剩下的拜託你了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:29.84,0:13:31.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你太卑鄙了 中校
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:44.78,0:13:46.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,結果 第二天早上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:46.45,0:13:48.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,她在自己的房裡醒來後
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:12.31,0:14:13.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,為什麼會有鬍鬚？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:16.55,0:14:17.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,沒了？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:18.12,0:14:22.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,附帶鬍鬚的重口味牛肉飯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:24.49,0:14:25.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,中校 不得了了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:25.86,0:14:28.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,昨天的遺失文明讓我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:34.20,0:14:37.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,果然性別被互換了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:38.00,0:14:41.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我的．．．我的胸部
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:43.38,0:14:46.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,性騷擾 這是性騷擾 佛特
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:46.41,0:14:48.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你是所有女性的敵人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:48.58,0:14:52.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我要在法庭上把現在看到的全都說出來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:52.65,0:14:54.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是這種話嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:54.35,0:14:57.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你們現在該講的是這種話嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:59.96,0:15:03.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,事情會變成這樣也是無可奈何的事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:03.70,0:15:08.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,總之 在恢復原狀之前 我想先保持這個樣子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:08.47,0:15:09.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:09.74,0:15:12.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,其實你們是在看好戲吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:12.81,0:15:14.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,最近一些不合理的事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:14.47,0:15:20.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,都習慣推給遺失文明或是政治腐敗造成的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:20.35,0:15:23.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,事情雖然看似解決
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:23.08,0:15:26.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,問題卻發生在別的地方
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:27.75,0:15:29.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,糟糕
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:29.09,0:15:31.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我把佛特最喜歡的杯子打破了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:34.76,0:15:35.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,怎麼了？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:35.86,0:15:37.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這個
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:37.36,0:15:41.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這個杯子啊 其實我已經厭倦了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:43.27,0:15:44.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你流血了喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:48.38,0:15:52.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不曉得會不會留下傷疤 去醫務室看看比較好喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:59.89,0:16:01.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這是什麼聲音？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:01.55,0:16:02.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,心臟？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:11.70,0:16:14.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,打開吧 打開吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:14.83,0:16:17.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,打開吧 打開吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:18.04,0:16:19.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,打開吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:20.81,0:16:21.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我是怎麼搞得
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:21.81,0:16:24.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,怎麼心裡小鹿亂撞聽 對方可是佛特耶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:28.78,0:16:31.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可惡 居然一個個的冒出來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:31.62,0:16:34.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這裡沒辦法應付了 跳下去吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:34.19,0:16:37.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這太扯了吧 而且太高了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:37.52,0:16:38.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你害怕嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:40.43,0:16:41.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不用害怕
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:47.60,0:16:49.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,對不起 佛特
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:49.10,0:16:51.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,都怪我受傷了才會這樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:51.34,0:16:52.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就是說嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:52.71,0:16:56.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,都是因為你的關係 把我搞得灰頭土臉的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:56.24,0:16:57.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,對不起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:59.31,0:17:02.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,白癡 不要當真啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:02.12,0:17:04.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不過 回去要請我喝杯酒喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:10.52,0:17:12.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,求求你們 不要再打了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:12.29,0:17:14.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,再打下去 佛特會死的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:14.83,0:17:16.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,別擔心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:16.76,0:17:19.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我的引擎現在才要開始發動呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:19.93,0:17:20.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,佛特
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:22.70,0:17:24.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,遲到了 遲到了 遲到了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:26.74,0:17:29.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你走路看哪裡啊 你這個冒失鬼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:31.21,0:17:34.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,抱歉 抱歉 粉紅色的草莓美眉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:34.95,0:17:35.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,色狼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:38.08,0:17:42.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,第361屆宇宙高中棒球大賽終於進行到最高潮
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:43.06,0:17:47.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,兩人出局滿壘 銀天高中隊能否渡過這個危機？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:50.06,0:17:51.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,佛特
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:53.60,0:17:54.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好球
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:55.90,0:17:58.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,受不了 真是熱昏了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:01.24,0:18:03.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,聽見了 聽見了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:03.31,0:18:05.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我聽見命運之鐘的聲音了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:06.75,0:18:11.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我和他的真愛故事終於要開始了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:13.32,0:18:14.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不要緊吧？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:15.32,0:18:18.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,一臉疲憊的樣子一點都不像你喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:22.50,0:18:26.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,她居然會打掃 這還真稀奇啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:28.87,0:18:30.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,怎麼回事？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:33.27,0:18:37.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,前略 佛特我和你在一起已經很久了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:37.74,0:18:40.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可是有這種心情這還是第一次
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:41.61,0:18:44.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你的聲音 你的舉止
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:44.32,0:18:47.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你所有的一切都讓我心頭發熱
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:47.99,0:18:50.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我已經無法再忍耐 已經是極限了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:50.12,0:18:51.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我要鼓起勇氣告訴你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:51.83,0:18:53.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,佛特 其實我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:53.93,0:18:54.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我愛你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:00.17,0:19:01.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,佛特
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:01.17,0:19:02.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,冷...冷靜點 蘭花
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:02.77,0:19:04.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我這種人有什麼好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:04.24,0:19:07.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你想因為一時的意亂情迷葬送你一生的幸福嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:07.71,0:19:12.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不是的我連睡覺都想到睡不著
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:12.21,0:19:16.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我以前遇見很多男性也談了很多戀愛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:16.12,0:19:18.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可是為什麼一直都不順利呢？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:18.99,0:19:21.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那是因為不論是強尼 湯姆還是尼可拉斯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:21.99,0:19:24.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他們都不是我命中注定的白馬王子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:25.99,0:19:30.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不是命中注定的人無法結合這是當然的 一點都沒錯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:30.76,0:19:34.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,因為我命中注定的人就在我的身邊啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:35.34,0:19:41.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,佛特 你能接受我的感情嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:43.64,0:19:44.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不要過來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:45.01,0:19:46.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,等一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:47.35,0:19:52.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,開...開什麼玩笑 這樣下去我身心都會變成男人的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:54.82,0:19:55.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,於是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:56.06,0:19:59.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,變成逃亡和追趕的兩個人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:01.53,0:20:03.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,從一個行星逃到另一個行星
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:03.30,0:20:04.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,從一個銀河逃到另一個銀河
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:04.86,0:20:07.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,持續著無窮無盡的逃亡生涯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:07.80,0:20:13.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,逃亡者的背後總有不死心的追兵身影
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:14.71,0:20:17.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,疲憊雖日漸累積
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:18.38,0:20:21.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但仍無法求得一個安住之地
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:23.02,0:20:28.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,最後只能逃到遙遠的邊境躲起來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:33.66,0:20:37.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,再怎麼會追 來到這裡應該沒問題了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:38.70,0:20:42.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,自己親手打毛衣啊 了不起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:42.34,0:20:44.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,一點都不像時下的年輕人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:44.97,0:20:47.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,算了！隨便你吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:51.64,0:20:54.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,謝謝 謝謝大家
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:54.51,0:20:57.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我們現在很幸福
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:58.45,0:21:00.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不論是你們健康的時候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:00.62,0:21:03.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,還是生病的時候都要健康地生病
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:03.72,0:21:05.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,應該說是未免病得太重了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:05.73,0:21:07.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那麼 請交換戒指
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:07.89,0:21:09.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,來吧 親愛的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:09.76,0:21:14.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,很久很久以前 在某個地方有一個老爺爺和一個老婆婆
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:14.80,0:21:16.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,怎麼了？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:16.07,0:21:19.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,快點把戒指戴在我手上啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:19.21,0:21:20.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,戒指？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:20.77,0:21:24.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我有更好的東西要給你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:29.82,0:21:32.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,為什麼我要跟男人結婚呢？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:35.76,0:21:37.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好美
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:37.12,0:21:37.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,小姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:38.06,0:21:42.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你才是我一直在尋找的人 嫁給我吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:42.66,0:21:43.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,慢著
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:44.73,0:21:49.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你們兩個在親熱什麼啊 混帳
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:49.34,0:21:54.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就是說嘛 應該大家一起交往才對啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:54.14,0:21:55.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你在胡扯些什麼啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:55.71,0:21:59.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這種事是先搶先贏
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:00.81,0:22:01.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不要
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:03.18,0:22:05.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那我就親自用身體來指導你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:05.92,0:22:07.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這我也不要
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:08.02,0:22:10.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,讓大叔為難的壞孩子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:13.56,0:22:17.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,原來如此 經過了這些事所以變成現在這樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:17.50,0:22:19.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那麼結論呢？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:19.27,0:22:23.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,低胰島素減肥法雖然有效 不過有很多副作用
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:23.70,0:22:24.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,沒興趣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:29.15,0:22:34.69,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Hey Boy What's up！エンジェル わっしょ～い！\NHey Boy What's up！Angel 哇咻！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:35.15,0:22:39.59,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,ふわふわアチチッ ケーキ大バクハツ！\N軟綿綿的好燙好燙 蛋糕大爆炸！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:39.66,0:22:40.71,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,ドンマイ！\NDon't mind！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:40.79,0:22:45.39,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,今日の運勢なに？晴れのち嵐！？\N今天運勢如何？晴後暴風雨！？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:45.46,0:22:46.45,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,マジで～？\N真的假的？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:46.53,0:22:51.13,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,悪のりサイコー！退屈バイバイ\N惡搞最棒！無聊Bye Bye
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:51.20,0:22:52.10,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,やっほー！\N呀呵！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:52.17,0:22:56.80,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,こっそり！知らんぷりで姑息な手段\N悄悄的！裝作若無其事用姑息的手段
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:56.87,0:22:58.03,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,神よ...\N神啊...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:58.64,0:23:00.74,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,休みの日は\N放假的日子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:00.81,0:23:03.44,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,はっぴ～ ウッキ～ のーてんき\NHappy 興奮 沒大腦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:03.51,0:23:04.64,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,着ぐるみ\N布偶娃娃裝
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:04.71,0:23:06.27,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,赤ちょうちん\N紅燈籠
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:06.35,0:23:08.48,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,デートがしたい！\N好想約會喔！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:08.55,0:23:10.75,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,お仕事です え～\N要工作啦 咦～
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:10.82,0:23:13.45,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,やーはっは 笑っちゃえ！\NYaHaHha 笑吧！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:13.52,0:23:16.29,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,ぷーんぷんぷん 怒っちゃえ！\NBumBumBum 生氣吧！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:16.36,0:23:19.23,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,うっしっし～とやり逃げ\NUSshiSshi 做了就逃
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:19.30,0:23:22.13,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,おっと Say アシカラズ\N海獅 請原諒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:22.20,0:23:24.89,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,えーんえんえん 泣きまね\NEnEnEn 裝哭
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:24.97,0:23:27.77,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,おーっほっほ 高笑い\NOHhoHho 放聲大笑
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:27.84,0:23:30.60,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,パ・パ・パとパラレル\NPaPaPa 滑雪橇
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:30.67,0:23:33.51,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,わっしょい☆パラダイス\N哇咻☆天堂
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:33.58,0:23:36.27,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,この世で一番！\N全世界第一！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:36.35,0:23:41.44,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,We are チャチャ チャンプ！\NWe are ChaCha Champ！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:42.45,0:23:47.44,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Hey Boy What's up！エンジェル わっしょ～い！\NHey Boy What's up！Angel 哇咻！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:48.35,0:23:54.44,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,See You バイバイ！サンキュー Good Luck！Hou！\NSee You Bye Bye！Thank You Good Luck！Hou！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:55.96,0:23:58.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那麼就來幫下一集做個「鬍子占卜」吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:59.83,0:24:01.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,首先是雙胞胎而且有鬍子的你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:01.37,0:24:03.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你的幸運物是義大利麵和韭菜
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:03.54,0:24:05.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,配菜不要忘了加上金箔跟綠寶石
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:06.01,0:24:06.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:06.64,0:24:07.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,拜託 你是雙胞胎嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:08.01,0:24:09.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不過我也沒有鬍子耶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:09.38,0:24:10.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,既然知道就不要回答
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:10.91,0:24:12.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,接著沒有鬍子的你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:12.25,0:24:14.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,醃菜是你最幸運的東西
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:14.08,0:24:16.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,能夠大幅提升你的金錢運和戀愛運
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:16.32,0:24:18.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,小心被圍著要簽名喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:18.25,0:24:19.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好 野餐是吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:19.39,0:24:20.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是醃菜啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:20.45,0:24:24.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,然後是上唇留著鬍子的人 你的存在感依然會很薄弱
